  "title": "Core Concepts",
  "lessonText": "This lesson introduces the fundamental concepts of Python programming essential for game development.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Python is an interpreted, high-level programming language.\n- It emphasizes code readability and simplicity.\n- Key concepts include variables, data types, control structures, and functions.\n- Python supports object-oriented programming, which is crucial for game development.\n- Understanding libraries and modules is important for expanding functionality."
